@model JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Common.Pagination.PagedResult<JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Clients.ClientSummary>
@inject JioCxRcsWrapper.Web.Services.PermissionUiService PermissionUi

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Clients";
    var canUpdate = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("Clients", "Update");
    var canDelete = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("Clients", "Delete");
}

<section class="page-hero panel-hero">
    <div>
        <div class="page-eyebrow">Client Onboarding</div>
        <h1>Agents & Brands</h1>
        <p>Manage onboarded JioCX agents, branding, and manager access.</p>
    </div>
    <a asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-primary panel-primary-btn">Create Client</a>
</section>

<section class="metric-strip">
    <article class="metric-tile">
        <span>Total Clients</span>
        <strong>@ViewBag.TotalClients</strong>
    </article>
    <article class="metric-tile">
        <span>Active Agents</span>
        <strong>@ViewBag.ActiveAgents</strong>
    </article>
</section>

<section class="panel-card mb-4">
    <div class="panel-card-header">
        <div>
            <h2>Filters</h2>
            <p>Filter clients by brand, agent, agent ID, or site.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <label class="form-label">Brand Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="BrandName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["BrandName"]" placeholder="Filter by brand..." />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <label class="form-label">Agent Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="AgentName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["AgentName"]" placeholder="Filter by agent..." />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <label class="form-label">Agent ID</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="AgentId" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["AgentId"]" placeholder="Filter by ID..." />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <label class="form-label">Site Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="SiteName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["SiteName"]" placeholder="Filter by site..." />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="panel-card">
    <div class="panel-card-header">
        <div>
            <h2>Client Directory</h2>
            <p>All agents visible in your current role scope.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    @if (TempData["ClientMessage"] is string message)
    {
        <div class="alert alert-success">@message</div>
    }
    @if (TempData["ClientError"] is string error)
    {
        <div class="alert alert-danger">@error</div>
    }
    <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table panel-table align-middle mb-0">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Brand Name</th>
                <th>Agent Name</th>
                <th>Agent ID</th>
                <th>Use Case</th>
                <th>Credits</th>
                <th>Credits</th>
                <th class="text-end action-cell">Actions</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            @foreach (var client in Model.Items)
            {
                <tr>
                    <td class="fw-semibold">@client.BrandName</td>
                    <td>@client.AgentName</td>
                    <td><code>@client.AgentId</code></td>
                    <td><span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">@client.AgentUseCase</span></td>
                    <td>@client.Credits</td>
                    <td class="text-end action-cell">
                        @if (canUpdate)
                        {
                            <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@client.Id" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Update</a>
                        }
                        @if (canDelete)
                        {
                            <form asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@client.Id" method="post" class="d-inline" onsubmit="return confirm('Delete this client?');">
                                @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger">Delete</button>
                            </form>
                        }
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <partial name="_Pager" model="Model" />
</section>
